== In popular culture ==
The purposes and authorship of &quot;The Federalist Papers&quot; were prominently highlighted in the lyrics of &quot;Non-Stop&quot;, the finale of Act One in the 2015 Broadway musical &quot;Hamilton&quot;, written by Lin-Manuel Miranda.

