This continued fraction would have infinite terms if and only if formula_23 is irrational, which is still unresolved.

==Known digits==
The number of known digits of Catalan&#x27;s constant has increased dramatically during the last decades. This is due both to the increase of performance of computers as well as to algorithmic improvements.

